is beschreibbar gemacht werden können.  afunded by Hans-Böckler-Stiftung  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-SA 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 4aBerlin. 4aEthnische Ökonomie. 4aIslam. 4aKulturanthropologie. 4aMarkt. 4aMigration. 4aMode. 4aSelbstständigkeit. 4aUnternehmertum. 4aUrban Studies. 4aWirtschaft. 4aWirtschaftssoziologie. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Anthropology / Cultural & Social.2bisacsh  aBerlin.  aCultural Anthropology.  aEconomic Sociology.  aEconomy.  aEntrepreneurship.  aEthnic Economy.  aFashion Studies.  aIslam.  aMarket.  aMigration.  aUrban Studies.2 aHans-Böckler-Stiftungefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2z978311076700108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Sociology 2022z9783110994520oZDB-23-DSL0 cprintz978383766081440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839460818?locatt=mode:legacyzOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839460818zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839460818/original  a978-3-11-076700-1 DG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2b2022  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2022  aZDB-23-DSLb2022  aZDB-23-GOA